Download latest wordpress setup from https://wordpress.org/download/
Unzip the setup file and rename that unzip folder to you site domain with extension
Move whole unzip folder to c://xampp/htdocs
run xampp
switch on the apache and mysql server 
open localhost/phpmyadmin on browser and create new database with usernme
then open http://localhost/dev2.techilaservices.com(site url)
Setup the wordpress site with all the details with non indexing checkbox(for not to crawl on google)
download new theme for wordpress site 
